<h1>YS is the best way to work with YAML</h1>

!!! note "Install `ys` Now!"

    ```bash
    curl -s https://yamlscript.org/install | BIN=1 bash
    [[ $PATH == *$HOME/.local/bin* ]] ||
      export PATH=~/.local/bin:$PATH

    ys --help
    ys -e 'say: "Hello, world!"'
    ```

